This is the IEEE_802_15_4_CustomBlocks-write-a-block package meant as a guide to building
out-of-tree packages. To use the IEEE_802_15_4_CustomBlocks blocks, the Python namespaces
is in 'IEEE_802_15_4_CustomBlocks', which is imported as:

    import IEEE_802_15_4_CustomBlocks

See the Doxygen documentation for details about the blocks available
in this package. A quick listing of the details can be found in Python
after importing by using:

    help(IEEE_802_15_4_CustomBlocks)
